  <lyrics>[V1]
 Iskay chunka qanchisniyoj
 Librosmanta yachasun.
 Mateo, Marcos, Lucas, Juan,
 Hechoswan, Romanoswan.
 
[C]
 Tukuyninchej yachanachej
 Diospa nisqan Bibliomanía.
 Chaypí kusiyta tarisun,
 Júchala atipasun.
 
[V2]
 Corintios, Gálatas; qhepan
 Efesios, Felipenses,
 Colonesensesman qhepampi
 Tesalonisensesman.
 
[V3]
 Timoteoman, qhepampi
 Titoman, Filemonman.
 Leenanchejpuni tíyan
 Hebreosman libreta.
 
[V4]
 Santiago, Pedro, Juanmanpis
 Qhepanta Judasmanpis.
 Apocalipsiswan tukun
 Mosoj Testamentoqa.
 
</lyrics></song>